high_descs: Turn around and face the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table on the right with the tomato.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Put the knife down to the left of the sliced tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right and walk to the counter space to the right of the stove.
Place the piece of tomato on the plate behind the apple.
Pick up the plate with the tomato.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Put the plate with the piece of tomato on the top shelf to the left of the lettuce and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and put a piece on a plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to go to the sink on your right.
Take the yellow-handled knife out of the right side of the sink.
Face the opposite direction and cross the room to the door, then turn right and go to the brown table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Put the knife down on the table, to the left of the tomato.
Take the slice from the right end of the tomato.
Turn right and go over to the sink, then right again and forward to the wall, then left to face the stove.
Put the piece of tomato on the plate near the back of the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the plate.
Go to the front of the fridge behind you.
Put the plate on the top fridge shelf, to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a plated slice of tomato into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right to go to the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go to the table on the other side on the right.
Slice the tomato resting on a fork on the table.
Place the knife on the table on the left of the tomato.
Take one slice of the tomato.
Turn around and go to the counter on the right side of the stove.
Place the tomato on the gray plate behind the apple
Pick up the plate with tomato on it
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the plate with tomato on it inside the refrigerator next to the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of tomato in the fridge
